AddCharset UTF-8 .txt

ErrorDocument 403 /pastes/403.txt
ErrorDocument 404 /pastes/404.txt

RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /

RewriteRule \.git/ - [F]
RewriteRule ^([A-Za-z0-9-]+)\.meta$ - [F]
RewriteRule ^pastes(/)$ /pastes/404.txt [L]
RewriteRule ^([A-Za-z0-9-]+)\.(txt|sh|php|py)$ pastes/$1.txt [L]

